Package com.milk.uberchat.iface

Interface Summary
ChatChannel This interface is what all chat channels must adhere to.
ChatChannelHolder This interface is for ChatLocus objects that also have an associated list of channels.
ChatEntity This interface represents any chat object that has an a name and a verbose description.
ChatIdentity This interface encapsulates a user identity, generally a particular userid on a particular chat system.
ChatLocus This interface represents any locus of users, including a chat identity, a channel on a chat system, and a user on a chat system.
ChatSystem This interface is what all chat systems must adhere to.
ChatSystemFactory This interface is for objects which can spew forth ChatSystems like there's no tomorrow.
ChatSystemTemplate This is the interface that all templates for ChatSystem creation must adhere to.
ChatUser This interface is what all chat users must adhere to.
